entries.llm_response:

  SELECT winner_id, COUNT(*) AS match_count
  FROM matches
  GROUP BY winner_id
),
max_winner AS (
  SELECT winner_id
  FROM winner_counts
  ORDER BY match_count DESC
  LIMIT 1
),
latest_ranking AS (
  SELECT r.player_id, r.ranking_points
  FROM rankings r

)

FROM max_winner mw
JOIN players p ON p.player_id = mw.winner_id
JOIN latest_ranking lr ON lr.player_id = mw.winner_id;
